理专家 原因：电子健康记录的普及和医疗数据分析的需求增加，推动了对健康信息管理专家的需求。 10. 机器人工程师 原因：自动化和机器人技术在制造业、物流等领域的应用扩展，推动了对机器人工程师的需求。 DeepSeek分析认为，这些岗位的高需求主要源于技术进步和行业变革，掌握相关技能的专业人士将有机会获得更高的薪酬和职业发展空间。"},"attached_info":"CkII+KHSvKnmvpQfEAMaCTExMzU2MTYxNCD17uC9BjAAOM8EQA5yCzEyOTMwNTk0OTEyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"57 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e03bb724b02e9626692be69c4fd940af_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1740525579.382162","card_id":"Q_302826029","target":{"id":302826029,"title":"李秋水作为一个生过孩子的人，怎么还能成为西夏的王妃呢？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/302826029","type":"question","created":1542528757,"answer_count":207,"follower_count":386,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4513,14229],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"无崖子人虚竹找的人是不是李秋水的妹妹？好像在书里面没有出现过？"},"attached_info":"Cj8I+KHSvKnmvpQfEAMaCDI5NTcxMDI2IPW9xN8FMAA4ggNAD3IJMzAyODI2MDI5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"54 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f29f8091c575171fe5c88dfbdc9a5a94_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"16_1740525579.382462","card_id":"Q_9960856998","target":{"id":9960856998,"title":"为什么大自然要把人类的寿命定在一百岁左右？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/9960856998","type":"question","created":1737219863,"answer_count":496,"follower_count":1881,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1136],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"每种生物的寿命似乎是自然根据种群的自然繁洐而规定好的，这种规定的机制和自然逻辑又是怎么样的，比如格陵兰鲨居然可以活600岁…"},"attached_info":"CkEI+KHSvKnmvpQfEAMaCTExMjk2ODI2MiCXvq+8BjAAONkOQBByCjk5NjA4NTY5OTh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_tex